Ruby Sparks;;2012;;R;;Comedy,Drama,Fantasy;;7.2;;Jonathan Dayton,Valerie Faris;;Paul Dano,Zoe Kazan,Annette Bening,Antonio Banderas,Chris Messina,Aasif Mandvi,Steve Coogan,Toni Trucks,Deborah Ann Woll,Elliott Gould,Alia Shawkat,Jane Anne Thomas,John F. Beach,Eleanor Seigler,Emma Julia Jacobs,Wallace Langham,Rightor Doyle,Eden Brolin;;Calvin is a genius novelist who begins to type a new novel on his manual typewriter about Ruby, his dream girl. He can't believe his eyes, because the next day, Ruby becomes a real person, and they begin to have a beautiful relationship together. If the relationship isn't perfect, all Calvin has to do is simply type the words on the page and Ruby's actions change to what he needs.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1839492/